Grumpy Moglin.Description: I spread laughter and joy once. It was awful.

Hate Hawk.Description: This is a BATTLE PET. Whoever that is trying to beat you up, this hawk HATES them!

Hooded Metal.Description: A cowled, iron mask - for those people who REALLY want to hide what they look like.

Hooded Skull.Description: A fiend's skull - what a great disguise.

Loremaster Pith Helmet.Description: Made of tough fibrous plants native to the Neverglades, this helm is resilient and practical. It also keeps the sun off pretty well.

Loremaster-In-Training.Description: If you want to be a Loremaster, you must know all there is to know about Lore. Yes, that's right. You must know Lore's lore. Until then, wear this to show your status as a Loremaster in training!

Lorestuck Battlemoglin.Description: Do this. No, not that, THIS. No! Why does everything have to be so complicated!?

Myths of Lore.Description: Maya drives a hard bargain for textbooks.

Nation's Paragon Helm.Description: A Paragon that's a member of the Nation? Interesting.

Necrotic Avenger.Description: You can see the smith's stamp on this. It was crafted by El_Rue. I do not know why that weird line is in his name. Must be a regionally specific grammar thing.

Necrotized Battle-helm.Description: The glow from your glaring crimson eyes will turn the courage in your opponents' hearts to brittle, dry dust.

Necrotized Broadsword Battle-Cape.Description: Although it should be enough to intimidate your opponents with just your glare and expressions, it never hurts to have a broadsword to back that challenging stare up.

Necrotized Claymore.Description: A blade among blades, wield this weapon well and your opponents will cower in fear and you tear through the field, rending your foes.

Necrotized Scythe.Description: The blade of this scythe is tipped with the razor-sharp obsidian claw of a darkness dragon and embellished with glaring skulls. It thirsts for the blood of your enemies.

Necrotized Warrior.Description: Embrace death and channel it to dominate your challengers and increase your battle prowess!

Nel the Librarian.Description: Being a librarian is not a cushy job in Lore. Field research can be, well, tricky sometimes. Librarians can't be afraid to get their hands dirty. Nel will help you with your research, as long as you've proven yourself.

NeoReaper Armor.Description: Neoreaper13 has crafted this color-customizable set for you in honor of your victories across Lore!

Netting.Description: A few well tied knots and bingo... ya got a net. Catch anything you like... from butterflies to burglars!

Night Masquerade.Description: After the hunt, it's traditional to celebrate with a masquerade ball.

Nimbo.Description: This is the type of dense cloud or cloud mass with ragged edges that yields rain... on you!

Noble Cloak.Description: This cloak has decorative designs along the trim. (color custom)

Noble Mage Armor.Description: Magic courses through your veins. Your arcane powers enable you to cast powerful spells.

Obake.Description: This strange little shapeshifting spirit seems to have been trapped in the form of a disquieting stuffed toy but insists on being used as a weapon. Suggested by AQW player El_Rue

Odanata Helm.Description: This a helm crafted from the discarded carapace of the Odanata, an insect race found on a distant world.

Ode to Joy Scythe.Description: It is SO happy! This is the most joyful weapon I've ever seen.

Orange Calligraphy Pen.Description: Write yourself into the history scrolls!

Original Healer Armor.Description: Healers are servants of good who use their powers to aid the sick, weak, and injured. Their powerful healing magic is often the difference between a group's victory or doom.

Original Mage Armor.Description: Magic courses through your veins. Your arcane powers enable you to cast powerful spells.

Original Rogue Armor.Description: Rogues follow their own set of rules. With a combination of speed, cunning and poisons, you take your enemies by surprise.

Original Warrior Armor.Description: The heart of a warrior is filled with courage and strength. Your skills with weapons in close combat make you a powerful force on the battlefield.

Ox-spicious far0.Description: This 2021, far0 wishes to be as strong as an ox. Will you help him?

Paladin's Vengeance.Description: Schillie, a noble and upright member of the Paladin's Order, wields this weapon to mete out justice across the land. Thanks to Yulgar's quick manufacturing, now you can wield a version of his sword, as well!

Paladin's Victory.Description: Crafted by the cunning and ever-victorious pikachu199519, this blade is awarded to Paladins who prove themselves most nobly in battle.

Pancake Battlemoglin.Description: I have no idea what you're talking about.

Pancake Moglin.Description: I have no idea what you're talking about.

Paper Plane.Description: It soars! It glides! It loops! By Schillie.

Paragon Fiend Quest Pet.Description: (This pet cannot be sold. It gives the same quests as Shogun Paragon Pet). Lurking in the darkness of the Underworld, this Paragon Fiend can actually help you!

Paragon Fiend Rider Pet.Description: This Paragon Fiend just refuses to leave his horse behind.

Parrot Pet.Description: Now you've got an attack parrot!

Pastel Nymph Wig.Description: A shimmering wig to make you look like a playful summer nymph!

Petrified Autumn Wood.Description: When Solrac was asked by the druids of the Cloister to create a weapon, he made this. Rather than forging a blade with hammer and anvil, he used his green thumb and grew this deadly weapon, making it a naturally lethal addition to anyone's arsenal.

Phantom Count.Description: Donning this outfit designed by Lock747, phantom counts have been haunting the castles that they used to occupy at one point. Just because you didn't see anyone there at first, doesn't mean that somebody wasn't already home.

Phantom's Curse.Description: A do sculpted and designed by Lock747, the phantom's curse is having to style their hair every single day!

Phazed Blade of Vengeance.Description: Designed by Lord Shadow, this dark blade pulses with a malevolent energy, and is augmented by futuristic technology which we do not quite understand yet.

Piercing Light.Description: An ancient gun repaired by your fellow player Reki after being lost in the sands of time. This combination of dagger and pistol collects sunlight and bends it into a concentrated beam of light. The mechanism to focus light is missing a piece, however.

Pile Of Logs.Description: It's never a great idea to chop wood inside; you run the risk of splinters!

Pile of Bones.Description: A pile of the finest sun bleached bones!

Pile of Fruit.Description: A small pile of fresh fruit. Apparently someone was hungry and took a bite out of the watermelon.

Pile of Skulls.Description: A pile of human skulls! This is not the way to get ahead in life.

Pink Bounty Hunter Blade.Description: Well if anything this might blind your opponents into submission.

Pink Calligraphy Pen.Description: A pink pen for the pinkest fan, Penolia! But why keep the power of the pen to just one hero? EVERYONE can write themselves into the history scrolls!

Pink Demonhunter Horns.Description: Beleen's love of pink can overcome even the strongest of beings - even Nulgath! Even his Demonhunters and Demonhuntresses are not immune.

Pink ShadowSlayer's Hat.Description: A replica of the real thing! Slay vampires, werewolves, and shadows with a stylish pink hat and a new 'do.

Why, t'was because the Cap'ns wished t'ambush Von Poach and his crew, o'course! But when ye are guided by a broken compass... prepare yerself for some tree-surfin'. Y'arr!

Pitcher Plant.Description: A pitcher plant from the faerie forest in Chiral Valley. It's beautiful and incredibly rare, too!

Planks.Description: A small group of wooden planks. The only way to safely walk the plank.

Plate of Golden Prowess.Description: Boldness, braveness, guts, fortitude, and heroism, rajab4 understood these qualities when forging this magnificent armor!

Pretty DOOMFire Warrior.Description: As a thanks for your eternal servitude to the Shadowscythe Empire, Beleen has dyed your DoomFire Warrior armor pink! (Requires DoomFire Warrior from 400k AC Achievement Badge Shop)

Pretty Pink DreadSaw.Description: Between the razor sharp blade and the pointed spikes this is not a weapon you wish to find yourself on the receiving end of... and then Beleen got ahold of it and turned it Pink!(Requires Iron Dreadsaw from Dirtlicker's Shop)

Pretty Pink Scarbucks Drink.Description: A nice big triple-shot latte to keep you warm as you battle. Be careful when ordering, you've seen what too much strawberry juice can do!

Pretty Sailor Mate.Description: All hands on deck! What is a ship without its crew? A large sea dwelling vessel - thats what!

Pretty Shimmering Flakes.Description: No, you don't need better shampoo--these pink, magical snowflakes will always fall, no matter what time of year it is!

Prof. Boylan's Bane.Description: As one of the most prestigious scientists of our time, Professor Boylan forged this great blade using complex mathematical formulas. This sword was granted to Lord Shadow for being the only pupil capable of figuring out Boylan's formula.

Pulsating Blade of Triumph.Description: After several years, Shaister1 harnessed a new source of energy. In doing so, he somehow contained this energy inside of a sword which has no foreseen end to the possible destruction it brings.

Pulsating Staff of Triumph.Description: Once Shaister1 harnessed this new energy, he decided to create a plethora of weapons to defeat his enemies. Since the blades need to be recharged overtime, the other end of the staff can be used for slaying foes when the pole is plugged in.

Purple Calligraphy Pen.Description: Write yourself into the history scrolls!

Purple Horse.Description: I herd you like purple horses! Have you ever seen a prettier one? NEIGH!

Pyromatic Katana.Description: Crafted by Lock747, the Pyromatic Katana is able to reach temperatures that rival the sun that heats Lore. With that thought in mind, just think of your next foe like a stick of butter...

Rabbit Ears.Description: I bet you can hear really good now. (color custom)

Rabbit Morph.Description: Your head has been polymorphed into a rabbit's head. You have a craving for carrots. (color custom)

Raging Fire Daggers.Description: Crafted by the mysterious Na Tra, these weapons will harness the fury inside of you and channel it into daggers of flame!

Rainbow Fro.Description: It's like a double rainbow of epicness as your hair!!!

Rainbow Ring Cape.Description: You will become a light of hope after the storm.

Rainbow Scythe.Description: Don't be fooled by it's vibrant colors, as this scythe will tear limb from limb...

Rapier.Description: Used in Europe in the 16th and 17th centuries. It is a relatively slender, sharply pointed sword, used mainly for thrusting attacks.

RazzleDazzle Daggers.Description: A pair of mammoth blades capable of taking out any threat, forged by your fellow player RazzleDazzle!

Reality's Judgement.Description: Reality really knows how to play the game... and the judgement was -- a custom staff as a reward for ALL to enjoy!

Reavers of Sakura.Description: Once the personal Magi of Alteon the Imbalanced, these mystical magic users now serve Gravelyn the Good.

Red Asian Dress.Description: A fashionable dress from the far east. (Girls only.)

Red Calligraphy Pen.Description: Write yourself into the history scrolls!

Red Moglin.Description: This isn't Twilly, but he had a roommate whose cousin's uncle was brothers with Twilly's aunt's nephew's Ear-Cleaning class teacher.

Red Parrot.Description: It's a red parrot on your shoulder!

Red Shell Turtle.Description: Slow and steady wins the battle!

Reki's Twin Dragons.Description: Reki knows his blades, and to prove it, he's crafted a dual-wielding sword set to showcase his skill. Bear them well, Hero!

Reminiscence.Description: Constructed by the infamous armor-crafter, Reki, your enemies will never forget you; in this life or the next.

Robe of the Arcane.Description: Tapping into arcane energy is a dangerous business indeed. Those that come close to mastering it are rewarded with unimaginable power.

Rock Egg.Description: Is it a rock or an egg?

Rogue Armor.Description: Rogues follow their own set of rules. With a combination of speed, cunning and poisons, you take your enemies by surprise.

Rogue Leather.Description: Rogue fighters prefer leather armor because it provides moderate protection without restricting their movement the way plate armor might.

Rolith's Hammer.Description: I'm sure he won't mind if you "borrow" his hammer for a little bit. I replaced the real one with a foam version. *snicker*

Rose Of The Fire Avatar.Description: For the most prismatic of all the staff, this lovely flame was gifted to Beleen who wants to share it with you!

Rose Petal Attire.Description: Celebrate the Season of Love with this gorgeous outfit seemingly made of red rose petals.

Rowan's Sword of Will.Description: He didn't deserve her mercy, but when she saved his life and became his weapon, not out of threats, but choice? Rowan now fights for her, instead of himself. Forged by Boxer502.

Royal Crown.Description: You better not let the king see you walking around with this color-customizable crown on!

Royal Fang Armor.Description: This regal armor embodies the savage ferocity of the wolves that roam Lore. Forged by Royal Knight, the Royal Fang Armor offers great protection while giving your enemies something to howl about!

Royal Fang Helm.Description: This golden armet, crafted by your fellow player Royal Knight, bears the teeth and mane of a mighty wolf, buffing your spirit with ferocity while showering your enemies with fear.

Royal Maximus.Description: Prince Knight, a royal son of Swordhaven, has fought bravely and proved himself in combat; he is a true hero of Lore. To commemorate his numerous victories, the Order of Paladins has commissioned this blade to share with all!

Royal Warrior's Helm.Description: Bow down before me or taste the sting of my blade. Crafted by the Hero that goes by Royal Knight.

Rune Falcon.Description: Zee the Legend journeyed long and far to acquire this enchanted blade. Combined with runes located at the opposite ends of Lore, this blade contains the power of a falcon's punch!

Runestone.Description: A magical runestone imported from Chiral Valley.

Runic Silence.Description: A mere whisper, traveling on the soft cool breeze of a summer night, is louder than this stealthy staff. Yet, silence is often more deadly than the loudest explosion.

Sack of Flour.Description: A large sack of flour locally milled. Perfect for all your baking needs!

Safiria's Castle.Description: The perfect place for Vampires to reside. This castle never sees the light of day--just the way you like it!

Sage the Purple Moglin.Description: For that special someone who must absolutely own everything in a shade of purple.

Sakura Blossom Attire.Description: Celebrate the Season of Love with this gorgeous outfit seemingly made of cherry blossoms.

Sakura Locks.Description: Celebrate the Season of Love with this gorgeous outfit seemingly made of cherry blossoms.

Sakura Shag.Description: Celebrate the Season of Love with this gorgeous outfit seemingly made of cherry blossoms.

Samarian.Description: Krom! These barbarians work as mercenaries and look to create their own kingdom. Their loyalties lie with no one but their own.

Samurai Armor.Description: This is the armor of a legendary warrior, whose faith, dedication and honor changed the way a whole nation thinks. Armor design inspired by RedWolf EADS.

Samurai Banner.Description: Wear this Samurai banner with the gold dragon emblem on it proudly!

Samurai Helmet.Description: Samurai armor was the most advanced armor for its time. Helmet design inspired by RedWolf EADS.

Samurai Katana.Description: The Katana was traditionally used by samurai from the 1400s onwards. Sword design inspired by RedWolf EADS.

Sands Of Blood Scythe.Description: Sanddemondude once saw a hieroglyphic of guards outside a royal chamber wielding a very strange scythe. Using the images as a base they crafted this scythe out of the recovered gems and gold found in the Sandsea.

Sarazen Armaments.Description: CervantesMaxi discovered this dagger embedded in the very bones of Lore. With massive strength, he ripped it from the rock and presents it to you as reminder of the power that one can wield if you only put your mind to it.

Scaled Egg.Description: A strange egg covered in scales. If it looks like this on the outside... then imagine what it looks like on the inside!!

Scarecrow Face.Description: This face will scare more than crows...

Scarecrow Hat.Description: A scarecrow doesn't really need a hat. You'll put it to better use.

Scarlet Sorceress Armor.Description: Blood Mages source their power from the blood in their veins. As for the Scarlet Sorceress, she focuses on the powers of her mirrors mixed in with Arcane energy. Absorbing life around her, mirroring all beauty into death.

Scarletta Helm.Description: Now you'll look as fabulous as the Sorceress herself, well okay maybe not as fabulous but close.

Scimitar.Description: A curved, single-edged sword of Oriental origin.

Scorpion Assassin Armor.Description: The Assassins of the Scorpion Order wear this armor.

Script of the Ox.Description: May this new year be filled with happiness, prosperity, and many precious moments with your loved ones. Happy Lunar New Year 2021!

Seafoam Nymph Wig.Description: A shimmering wig to make you look like a playful summer nymph!

Seafoam Sprite Wig.Description: Put on this wig to look like a playful summer sprite!

Sepulchure's Undead Blade.Description: This sword hungers for destruction... are you sure you can control such dark energy?

Seraph Avenger.Description: You can see the smith's stamp on this. It was crafted by El_Rue. I do not know why that weird line is in his name. Must be a regionally specific grammar thing.

Seraphic Fortress.Description: A fortress fit only for the most loyal of Laken's followers. Only the most worthy Seraphic Paladins will truly feel at home.

Sergeant Snipps the Barber.Description: Sergeant Snipps of the Moglin Barber Brigade is eager to travel with you! (And keep an eye on his hairstyle; it will change randomly in the future.) He wants to make sure you look your best before - and after - every battle!

Serpentic Edge.Description: Be as dexterous as the curves of your blade are smooth and you'll dance through battles, slashing and slicing without injury.

Shadow Breather.Description: Once it wears its blindfold, it will remove its mouth cover. Opening his mouth, he breathes an immense amount of shadow which will envelop the entire place in total darkness, enabling him to assassinate his opponent. His blades never shine for maximum stealth. --Ninjudo

Shadow Breather Mask.Description: Masking your face, you become an unknown face in the dark. None will know who you are, assuming they even see you first...

Shadow Breather Odango.Description: Keeping your hair tied back is essential in combat. It could obstruct your view of your prey. Masking the rest of your head, your opponent will not be granted the knowledge of their opponent...

Shadow Conqueror Helm.Description: A devious helm suited for Conquerors with a crest that matches your unnatural hair color.

Shadow Ghoul.Description: No one knows what the Shadow Ghoul is. Undead... living... all we know is that it is something not from this world. This fully color-custom monstrosity was discovered by your fellow player, Kris Clean.

Shadow of the Rainbow.Description: Tasked with keeping the secrets of the Rainbow hidden from the outside world, The Shadow of the Rainbow know both the glory and pain that can stem from Rainbows. If these secrets were ever revealed, all of Lore would be DOOMED!!!

Shadow's Edge.Description: Crafted by Aeoden, this steel blade has the power to call the shadows, but it is up to you to command them. If you do not have the strength of will to control them... they will devour you!

Shadowed Caster Locks.Description: Dage's promise fulfilled to his Undead Legion.

Shadowed Caster Morph.Description: Dage's promise fulfilled to his Undead Legion.

Shadowed Soul Weaver.Description: Souls wander throughout the Underworld. Only the most skilled can channel the power that remains, using them for arcane spells and magic.

Shamshir.Description: A Persian type of sabre with a curve that is considered radical for a sword.

Shattered Ice.Description: This is one coooooool scythe! Inspired by xHAKOx suggestion and art done by Pinwheel.

Sheathed FlameBlade Blade.Description: The heat from these will keep the most reclusive assassin warm.

Shimmering Silence.Description: Every Silent Sentinel needs a trusty weapon that can be depended on at a moment's notice. We present to you the Shimmering Silence, the chosen sword of the Silent Sentinel. Raw power pulses, illuminating the runes on the blade, emitting a silent warning to all those who lay eyes on it.

Shining Knight's Helmet.Description: Forged by Coolboypai, this helm will protect those that are willing to protect the less fortunate. Always remember that there is good still in some of us and you are that driving force.

Shocking Pink Caster Staff.Description: This staff holds powerful magic of Pink Star light!

Silent Sentinel.Description: Standing resolute and waiting, the Silent Sentinel has the discipline to wait for the most opportune time to strike. Just... don't walk in front of the Hero that wears this armor and make funny faces to try and distract him or her. We can't be held liable for what ensues.

Zard.Description: Lore has MANY zards, and now you can battle alongside one of your own!
